dct_title_s: Mineral map of Lake County, California
dct_description_sm: issued by California State Mining Bureau ; Lewis E. Aubury, State Mineralogist.
Shows township and section lines, ranchos, creeks and rivers, ridges, lakes, and springs.
Locations of mines and mineral deposits are numbered but not named on map.
